| count(*) | cast(a as char)     | cast(b as char) | cast(c as char)         |
+----------+---------------------+-----------------+-------------------------+
|        1 | 2021-04-13 00:34:00 | 2021-04-13      | 2021-04-13 00:34:00.123 |
